*** ChanServ Help - Command: SET NEVEROP ***
Enables or disables the Never Op option for a channel.
If it is enabled, AOPs and up will not be automatically
opped by ChanServ upon joining the channel.
 
Syntax:
/cs SET #channel NEVEROP <ON|OFF>
 
Examples:
/cs SET #IRCHelp NEVEROP ON
/cs SET #Services NEVEROP OFF
 
Type /join #IRCHelp for more information.
*** End of Help ***